### Session Advanced API Tests
### Tests for SessionAdvancedController endpoints
### Base URL: http://localhost:8080
### OpenCode server: http://localhost:4096

### Fork a session
### Creates a copy of an existing session at a specific point
# @prompt sessionId Replace with actual session ID
POST http://localhost:8080/api/sessions/advanced/{{sessionId}}/fork
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message_id": "message_uuid_to_fork_from"
}

###

### Revert session to previous state
### Reverts a session to a specific message or state
# @prompt sessionId Replace with actual session ID
POST http://localhost:8080/api/sessions/advanced/{{sessionId}}/revert
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message_id": "message_uuid_to_revert_to"
}

###

### Get session share link
### Generates a shareable link for the session
# @prompt sessionId Replace with actual session ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/sessions/advanced/{{sessionId}}/share
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Summarize session
### Generates a summary of the session conversation
# @prompt sessionId Replace with actual session ID
POST http://localhost:8080/api/sessions/advanced/{{sessionId}}/summarize
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message_id": "optional_message_id_to_summarize_from"
}

###

### Get session children
### Returns child sessions forked from this session
# @prompt sessionId Replace with actual session ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/sessions/advanced/{{sessionId}}/children
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Execute command in session
### Executes a command within the session context
# @prompt sessionId Replace with actual session ID
POST http://localhost:8080/api/sessions/advanced/{{sessionId}}/command
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "command": "build",
  "parts": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "Run the build command"
    }
  ]
}

###

### Execute shell command in session
### Executes a shell command within the session
# @prompt sessionId Replace with actual session ID
POST http://localhost:8080/api/sessions/advanced/{{sessionId}}/shell
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "command": "ls -la"
}

###
